================================================================================
Scope of this license for LabProc
================================================================================

This CC BY 4.0 license applies to:
  - Annotations (annotations/op_master.csv and any future *_master.csv files)
  - Per-task benchmark item CSVs (benchmark_items/*.csv)
  - Source video URL manifest (manifests/source_videos.csv)
  - Evaluation harness scripts (evaluation/*.py)
  - Annotation skill prompt (evaluation/annotation_skill_prompt.md)
  - Controlled vocabularies (evaluation/controlled_vocabulary.json)
  - Dataset card (README.md)
  - Croissant metadata (croissant.json)

This license does NOT apply to:
  - Source video files referenced by the URL manifest. Those videos
    are hosted on YouTube and are subject to YouTube's Terms of
    Service and the original creators' chosen licenses. The LabProc
    release does not redistribute source video files; users are
    responsible for reviewing each video's upstream license before
    use.

